", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1324}, {\"ngram\": \"that strength\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"the big boy\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1404}, {\"ngram\": \"medal contention\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His success on the Olympic stage is all the more remarkable given his struggle with injuries, which began as a child after being diagnosed with Perthes' disease, meaning he was unable to do sport for three years.\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1610, \"end\": 1626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Legg\\u2013Calv\\u00e9\\u2013Perthes_disease\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Perthes' disease\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Legg\\u2013Calv\\u00e9\\u2013Perthes_disease\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Legg\\u2013Calv\\u00e9\\u2013Perthes_disease\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His success\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1477}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic stage\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"his struggle\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"a child\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1661}, {\"ngram\": \"three years\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hepworth also revealed he had been struggling with a back issue earlier this year.\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1762, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hepworth\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1688}, {\"ngram\": \"a back issue\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"I think it was around February I had a stress response in my back so I could not do floor for four months and had to take a month off vault not too long ago as well because of the same thing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1804}, {\"ngram\": \"