ike to say thank you to my coaches, they have put so many hours into me.\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my coaches\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2366}, {\"ngram\": \"so many hours\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I could never have paid them.\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2434, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And my girlfriend and her family.\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2468, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"And my girlfriend\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2452}, {\"ngram\": \"her family\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So thankful.\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If I can get a bronze medal at the Olympics, I should be able to pass my test.\\\"\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2563, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2511}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2527}, {\"ngram\": \"my test\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hepworth's team-mateJake Jarmanfinished fourth in the vault after a strong finale from Davtyan meant he slipped out of the podium positions.\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2705, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the vault\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2624}, {\"ngram\": \"a strong finale\", \"from\": 2631, \"to\": 2646}, {\"ngram\": \"Davtyan\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2659}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium positions\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2704}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-year-old had claimed his first Olympic medal and Britain's first in artistic gymnastics this Games on Saturday with bronze on the floor and admitted the standard of the vault competition has increased.\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his first Olympic medal\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2758}, {\"ngram\": \"artistic gymnastics\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2801}, {\"ngram\": \"this Games\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2812}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2824}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2836}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2849}, {\"ngram\": \"the standard\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2875}, {\"ngram\": \"the vault competition\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 2900}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"To be honest even though I missed out, I think the average score I got was definitely better than qualifiers and it's very consistent if you look at the competitions I have competed in over the last few years.\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 3136, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the average score\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 2991}, {\"ngram\": \"qualifiers\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3035}, {\"ngram\": \"the competitions\", \"from\": 3076, \"to\": 3092}, {\"ngram\": \"the last few years\", \"from\": 3117, \"to\": 3135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think I became European champ in 2022 with a similar score.\", \"from\": 3138, \"to\": 3200, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"European champ\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3170}, {\"ngram\": \"a similar score\", \"from\": 3184, \"to\": 3199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It shows I am still consistent on the piece of apparatus, it's just the level of it has increased, you have got more people who can score those high averages.\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the piece\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3244}, {\"ngram\": \"apparatus\", \"from\": 3248, \"to\": 3257}, {\"ngram\": \"the level\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3278}, {\"ngram\": \"more people\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3324}, {\"ngram\": \"those high averages\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It means to myself that I just need to up my game a little bit.\", \"from\": 3361, \"to\": 3425, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my game\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3411}]}, {\"sentence\": \